      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How do you target the right people with church Facebook ads?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Start with geographic targeting within a reasonable drive radius of your church (typically 10-15 miles). Layer in interest-based targeting such as Christianity, church, family, and community involvement. The O2F Method teaches a specific targeting framework that identifies people most likely to visit your church this Sunday."
